title: Bobby’s Top 5 TV Show Of All-Time + Dr. Oz Answers Our Questions About Energy Drinks, Chiropractors and Bobby’s Colonoscopy + Morgan2 Turns 28…Thinks Someone Put Something In Her Drink Over The Weekend
itunes:title: Bobby’s Top 5 TV Show Of All-Time + Dr. Oz Answers Our Questions About Energy Drinks, Chiropractors and Bobby’s Colonoscopy + Morgan2 Turns 28…Thinks Someone Put Something In Her Drink Over The Weekend
description:
Bobby said earlier this week that “Squid Games” may be his favorite TV Show of all time. So he shares the list he made of his definite Top 5 TV shows of all-time. We talked to Dr. Oz and he answers all of our health questions including a very personal one Bobby has about his upcoming colonoscopy. We wish Morgan2 a Happy Birthday! She tells us about how she fell down some stairs over the weekend at her celebration and thinks someone may have put something in her drink.
